Title: 4 Film Favorites: Harrison Ford (The Fugitive / Presumed Innocent / Firewall / The Mosquito Coast)

reviewText: I enjoyed every movie in this set. The Fugitive, Presumed innocent, and Firewall I have seen several times. Harrison Ford brings a intensity to the role he plays in each movie of this set.  Mosquito Coast is  not the equal of the other three films, but the character Ford plays in this movie is perhaps the most complex. It is not difficult to identify with this man who loves his family and wants disparately to protect them from what he perceives as the decay of American society.  There is nothing he will not sacrifice for them. This four movie set is well worth the price, and definitely worth adding to your collection.
summary: This four movie collection of Harrison Ford movies is a definate buy.

Title: 4 Film Favorites: Harrison Ford (The Fugitive / Presumed Innocent / Firewall / The Mosquito Coast)

reviewText: I bought this to expand our movie collection, and just becaue I like this actor's movies in general. I had not seen Mosquito Coast before, in large part because the title didn't much appeal to me, but I watched it once I got this collection. All I can say is, wow. It's a movie that intrigues you and also puts you on edge and keeps you there through the whole picture. The Fugitive was a familiar movie to me as I've seen it a couple of times before, and never get tired of it. Presumed innocent will certainly keep you on the edge of your seat, as will Firewall, another film I failed to see when it first came out. I'm glad I bought these for our collection.
Title: 4 Film Favorites: Harrison Ford (The Fugitive / Presumed Innocent / Firewall / The Mosquito Coast)
